.TH "wait_and_poll" 9 "wait_and_poll" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
wait_and_poll \- Issues a polling command
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" wait_and_poll
.BI "(struct megasas_instance *instance "  ","
.BI "struct megasas_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "int seconds "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "instance" 12
Adapter soft state
.IP "cmd" 12
Command packet to be issued
.IP "seconds" 12
Maximum poll time
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
For polling, MFI requires the cmd_status to be set to 0xFF before posting.
